Say '''Pontevedra''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Capiz]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 43,525 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 130.9 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 5802.	
															
